Issue to Resolution – Complete Flow
🔴 Issue Observed
Service: osqar-qualification-manager
Environment: UAT
Problem:
Application health checks were failing intermittently
Liveness probe had timeoutSeconds = 1
This is too low → app not responding within 1 sec → pod may restart unnecessarily
🔍 Initial Investigation
Checked HPA:
Bash
kubectl get hpa -n ibwv-uat-osqar | grep osqar-qualification-manager
✔ Found HPA exists
✔ CPU usage was very low (0%) → no scaling issue
Verified Pods:
Bash
kubectl get pods -n ibwv-uat-osqar | grep osqar-qualification-manager
✔ Pods were running
❗ But issue likely due to probe timeout, not pod crash
Checked Deployment YAML:
Bash
kubectl get deploy osqar-qualification-manager -n ibwv-uat-osqar -o yaml
Found:
YAML
livenessProbe:
  periodSeconds: 10
  timeoutSeconds: 1   ❌ (too low)
⚠️ Root Cause
timeoutSeconds: 1
👉 Application not responding within 1 sec
👉 Kubernetes marks container unhealthy
👉 Can cause unnecessary restarts / false failures
🛠️ Fix Applied
Edited deployment directly:
Bash
kubectl edit deploy osqar-qualification-manager -n ibwv-uat-osqar
Changed:
YAML
timeoutSeconds: 1  →  5   ✅
✔ As suggested by team (safe incremental change)
✔ Did NOT change periodSeconds (kept as 10)
🚀 Deployment Behavior
After saving:
Kubernetes automatically triggered rollout
Old pods terminated
New pods created with updated config
✅ Verification
Checked pods again:
Bash
kubectl get pods -n ibwv-uat-osqar | grep osqar-qualification-manager
✔ New pods started (~3 min age)
✔ Status = Running
✔ Ready = 1/1
(Optional validation)
Bash
kubectl get deploy osqar-qualification-manager -n ibwv-uat-osqar -o yaml | grep timeoutSeconds
✔ Confirmed value updated to 5
🎯 Final Outcome
Liveness probe timeout increased from 1s → 5s
Pods restarted successfully
No failures observed after deployment
Service is stable
🟢 Key Learnings
Very low timeoutSeconds can cause false health failures
Always increase gradually (1 → 5, not directly 30)
kubectl edit deploy automatically triggers rollout
Pod restart confirms config change applied
🗣️ One-line Summary (for Lead / Interview)
👉
“Identified that liveness probe timeout was too low (1s), updated it to 5s, which triggered a rollout, and verified new pods are running successfully without issues.”